302
00:23:53,460 --> 00:23:55,740
Money makes everything easier.

303
00:24:02,640 --> 00:24:03,759
I'll get your cash.

304
00:24:04,839 --> 00:24:05,660
Wait for my call.

305
00:24:08,579 --> 00:24:09,619
If you so much as look at her...

306
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:12,900
you'll never

307
00:24:14,559 --> 00:24:16,160
see those files. EVER!

308
00:24:22,900 --> 00:24:23,779
Look at you.

309
00:24:25,279 --> 00:24:26,700
Learning how to

310
00:24:27,859 --> 00:24:29,220
play the game.

311
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:33,119
If you didn't ask for the cash,

312
00:24:33,779 --> 00:24:34,640
I'd have thought

313
00:24:34,640 --> 00:24:36,339
you were a rat.

314
00:25:10,519 --> 00:25:10,880
Hey,

315
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:13,440
Zhai is here.

316
00:25:14,759 --> 00:25:15,660
Get your team ready.

317
00:25:18,720 --> 00:25:20,259
[How could you tamper with]

318
00:25:20,539 --> 00:25:21,339
[my college application!]

319
00:25:24,420 --> 00:25:25,460
[There's 80 grand.]

320
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:26,519
[It'll get you started.]

321
00:25:27,500 --> 00:25:28,140
[You told me]

322
00:25:28,140 --> 00:25:29,039
[we were in the clear!]

323
00:25:29,359 --> 00:25:29,759
[Why are you]

324
00:25:29,759 --> 00:25:30,700
[trying to get rid of me?]

325
00:25:36,180 --> 00:25:37,539
[Because I'm]

326
00:25:37,539 --> 00:25:38,059
[sick of this.]

327
00:25:39,039 --> 00:25:40,000
[We don't belong together.]

328
00:25:40,980 --> 00:25:41,779
[You're deadweight.]

329
00:25:42,240 --> 00:25:43,799
[Are you serious?]

330
00:25:44,039 --> 00:25:45,460
[Do you even hear yourself?]

331
00:25:52,000 --> 00:25:53,000
[I know what I'm doing.]

332
00:25:54,220 --> 00:25:54,720
[It's time]

333
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:57,140
[you stop living in a fantasy.]

334
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:05,440
[Disappointed?]

335
00:26:14,559 --> 00:26:15,119
[Chen Yi,]

336
00:26:17,700 --> 00:26:18,579
[you're gonna regret this.]

337
00:26:35,579 --> 00:26:36,140
[Yi,]

338
00:26:37,420 --> 00:26:38,640
[we're closing in on them.]

339
00:26:39,460 --> 00:26:40,900
[You didn't have to break her heart.]

340
00:26:43,420 --> 00:26:43,940
[if she's here,]

341
00:26:45,460 --> 00:26:46,119
[I can't keep her safe.]

342
00:27:01,859 --> 00:27:02,460
[Chen Yi!]

343
00:27:24,019 --> 00:27:24,779
[Hey,]

344
00:27:26,259 --> 00:27:27,700
[sorry about the head.]

345
00:27:30,019 --> 00:27:30,980
[But look,]

346
00:27:31,700 --> 00:27:33,099
[I did some thinking,]

347
00:27:33,599 --> 00:27:34,640
[and staying here]

348
00:27:35,319 --> 00:27:35,960
[is suicide.]

349
00:27:37,059 --> 00:27:37,859
[I'm setting us up]

350
00:27:37,859 --> 00:27:39,099
[in a new spot.]

351
00:27:40,700 --> 00:27:42,000
[Once we strike gold over there,]

352
00:27:42,220 --> 00:27:43,859
[we're gonna roll back like kings!]

353
00:27:45,500 --> 00:27:46,279
[You trying to say something?]

354
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:48,380
[Where the hell... are you taking me?]

355
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:49,779
[Jinguo.]

356
00:27:50,339 --> 00:27:51,140
[Very close.]

357
00:27:51,480 --> 00:27:52,559
[We'll be there before you know it.]

358
00:27:58,220 --> 00:28:00,700
[Just get some rest, kid.]

359
00:28:14,259 --> 00:28:14,900
[Alright,]

360
00:28:15,359 --> 00:28:16,160
[it's done.]

361
00:28:16,460 --> 00:28:17,299
[Just as you planned.]

362
00:28:18,220 --> 00:28:18,880
[Y'know,]

363
00:28:19,799 --> 00:28:20,960
[leaving this kid]

364
00:28:21,599 --> 00:28:22,700
[running around]

365
00:28:23,039 --> 00:28:24,500
[is a ticking]

366
00:28:24,759 --> 00:28:25,579
[time bomb.]

367
00:28:25,819 --> 00:28:26,680
[Taking him is the smart move.]

368
00:28:27,339 --> 00:28:28,059
[You're right.]

369
00:28:29,180 --> 00:28:29,940
[I'd worry about you]

370
00:28:29,940 --> 00:28:30,779
[out there alone.]

371
00:28:32,299 --> 00:28:33,259
[I'll handle]

372
00:28:34,259 --> 00:28:34,940
[the ledger.]

373
00:28:36,279 --> 00:28:37,140
[Once the dust settles,]

374
00:28:37,940 --> 00:28:38,940
[I'll bring you back home myself.]

375
00:28:39,779 --> 00:28:40,319
[Sounds good.]

376
00:28:41,079 --> 00:28:41,440
[Watch your back.]

377
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:44,839
[Always do.]

378
00:30:09,680 --> 00:30:10,319
Chen Yi,

379
00:30:12,720 --> 00:30:14,240
just level with me.

380
00:30:14,920 --> 00:30:15,680
What did Zhou Kangan

381
00:30:15,680 --> 00:30:16,980
actually promise you?

382
00:30:18,660 --> 00:30:19,180
Money?

383
00:30:19,519 --> 00:30:20,039
Or...

384
00:30:20,440 --> 00:30:20,920
a clean slate?

385
00:30:21,140 --> 00:30:22,099
I could have offered way more.

386
00:30:23,460 --> 00:30:24,940
Why the hell

387
00:30:26,480 --> 00:30:27,799
did you stab me

388
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:28,799
in the back?

389
00:30:32,859 --> 00:30:33,720
It's simple.

390
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,319
I was never

391
00:30:37,619 --> 00:30:39,119
a monster like you.

392
00:30:39,319 --> 00:30:40,240
Naive sonuvab*tch!

393
00:30:45,220 --> 00:30:46,920
Money's the only goddamn thing that's real!

394
00:30:50,819 --> 00:30:52,660
Is that what you told yourself

395
00:30:55,140 --> 00:30:56,059
when you set up

396
00:30:57,299 --> 00:30:58,599
your ride-or-die

397
00:30:58,599 --> 00:31:00,259
to take the fall for you?

398
00:31:12,539 --> 00:31:14,380
So you knew the whole story.

399
00:31:19,859 --> 00:31:20,779
No wonder

400
00:31:21,779 --> 00:31:22,900
you acted so sketchy

401
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:24,720
when you got back

402
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:25,740
to Vineton.

403
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:37,980
I started

404
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:42,279
in the grease with Zhai.

405
00:31:43,420 --> 00:31:44,740
First we were nobody.

406
00:31:45,480 --> 00:31:48,039
Then we were the guys

407
00:31:49,500 --> 00:31:50,740
you don't mess with.

408
00:31:52,799 --> 00:31:53,880
Now, I run this town.

409
00:31:58,460 --> 00:31:59,140
Now,

410
00:32:00,619 --> 00:32:02,140
every witness to my past

411
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:03,680
is buried.

412
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:05,599
Except you.

413
00:32:07,480 --> 00:32:08,079
Yi,

414
00:32:09,240 --> 00:32:10,759
you're done.

415
00:32:12,400 --> 00:32:13,279
Any regrets?

416
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:19,160
You got He Wenjie killed.

417
00:32:21,339 --> 00:32:22,299
You built your "empire"

418
00:32:22,299 --> 00:32:23,960
on the bones of this city.

419
00:32:27,420 --> 00:32:29,240
You're not a king.

420
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:31,799
You're just

421
00:32:32,299 --> 00:32:33,559
a glorified parasite.

422
00:32:34,160 --> 00:32:34,920
Do you feel sick

423
00:32:36,599 --> 00:32:37,539
looking in the mirror?

424
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:43,779
I told you, kid.

425
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:47,039
I own an empire because

426
00:32:49,019 --> 00:32:50,420
I dared to bet big.

427
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:53,519
I'd do it all over again!

428
00:33:09,220 --> 00:33:10,740
Since you wanna be a martyr...

429
00:33:13,339 --> 00:33:13,960
Hey,

430
00:33:15,279 --> 00:33:15,720
look at me!

431
00:33:16,500 --> 00:33:16,940
Go

432
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:18,539
to hell

433
00:33:18,920 --> 00:33:19,720
and regret it there!

434
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:41,500
[Silly boy,]

435
00:33:41,500 --> 00:33:42,220
[go wash your hands,]

436
00:33:42,420 --> 00:33:43,160
[dinner's ready.]

437
00:33:46,279 --> 00:33:47,240
[Mom...]

438
00:34:07,779 --> 00:34:09,219
Zhang Bin is too smart

439
00:34:10,099 --> 00:34:11,519
to get cornered

440
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:13,559
without a way out.

441
00:34:14,440 --> 00:34:15,179
He's gotta be waiting for

442
00:34:15,179 --> 00:34:16,360
Liu's guys to pick him up.

443
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:17,519
Move!

444
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:19,280
We gotta find him.

445
00:34:36,940 --> 00:34:37,940
Everyone's

446
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,820
terrified of dying.

447
00:34:41,039 --> 00:34:42,559
I thought you were made of tougher stuff.

448
00:34:52,659 --> 00:34:54,300
Even the executioner

449
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:58,179
gets cold feet.

450
00:35:10,199 --> 00:35:10,920
Still acting tough?

451
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:12,320
Alright.

452
00:35:14,300 --> 00:35:15,099
Outta respect for our old days,

453
00:35:16,260 --> 00:35:17,280
I'll buy you

454
00:35:20,500 --> 00:35:22,340
a nice tombstone.

455
00:35:25,460 --> 00:35:26,300
See you in hell, kid!

456
00:35:30,079 --> 00:35:30,639
Chen Yi!

457
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:32,300
Oh my god...

458
00:35:32,300 --> 00:35:32,920
Jing...

459
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:34,239
Leave...

460
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:35,679
Now!

461
00:35:40,559 --> 00:35:41,079
Jing...

462
00:35:43,579 --> 00:35:44,300
Run!

463
00:36:08,579 --> 00:36:09,179
Chen Yi!

464
00:36:21,239 --> 00:36:21,619
Move your a**!

465
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:26,780
Right here!

466
00:37:39,179 --> 00:37:40,400
Saved by the bell.

467
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:41,500
This is

468
00:37:41,500 --> 00:37:42,760
where we part ways!

469
00:38:18,880 --> 00:38:20,260
Miss me, brother?

470
00:38:21,300 --> 00:38:23,699
Time to settle up!

471
00:38:23,980 --> 00:38:24,360
Zhai...

472
00:38:25,079 --> 00:38:25,539
Oh, Jesus...

473
00:38:48,579 --> 00:38:50,079
[Right before they shipped me off,]

474
00:38:51,480 --> 00:38:53,000
[Zhai had me chained at the harbor.]

475
00:38:55,159 --> 00:38:55,920
[Funny thing is...]

476
00:38:57,659 --> 00:38:58,780
[I wasn't scared at all.]

477
00:39:01,099 --> 00:39:02,000
[My only regret was]

478
00:39:03,739 --> 00:39:05,059
[leaving you without kissing you goodbye]

479
00:39:07,440 --> 00:39:08,559
[or]

480
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,320
[feeling your touch like this.]

481
00:39:20,699 --> 00:39:21,300
[Chen Yi,]

482
00:39:24,960 --> 00:39:25,820
[you belong to me.]

483
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,000
No!

484
00:40:38,179 --> 00:40:38,559
Please!

485
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:39,280
Oh God!

486
00:40:40,000 --> 00:40:40,820
Stop it!

487
00:40:41,159 --> 00:40:41,960
I'm begging you!

488
00:40:55,739 --> 00:40:56,300
Don't

489
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:57,320
do this!

490
00:40:58,579 --> 00:40:59,059
SWAT!

491
00:40:59,179 --> 00:40:59,639
Nobody move!

492
00:40:59,639 --> 00:41:00,739
Hands on your head!

493
00:41:01,019 --> 00:41:01,559
Put the knife down!

494
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,040
Drop the knife!

495
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:03,640
Do it now!

496
00:41:03,640 --> 00:41:03,720
Or we will fire!

497
00:41:03,980 --> 00:41:04,519
I'll live,

498
00:41:04,940 --> 00:41:05,900
man.

499
00:41:28,079 --> 00:41:28,539
Jing!

500
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:29,500
Hey!

501
00:41:30,739 --> 00:41:31,159
Yi!

502
00:41:31,460 --> 00:41:32,019
Stay with me!

503
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:33,760
Get the paramedics!

504
00:41:34,139 --> 00:41:35,380
Call an ambulance!

505
00:42:35,440 --> 00:42:36,380
I...

506
00:42:37,460 --> 00:42:38,500
LOVE...

507
00:42:40,340 --> 00:42:41,340
YOU...

508
00:42:43,300 --> 00:42:44,199
I LOVE YOU...

509
00:42:44,480 --> 00:42:45,639
EVEN MORE...
